      "text": "Design a chat system",
      "fontSize": 27.333331298828128,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Design a chat system",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "K-yLzgTZ6t83pAR9KgfeQ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 249,
      "y": 185,
      "width": 452.4797668457031,
      "height": 650,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a2",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1606484751,
      "version": 611,
      "versionNonce": 525115331,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1765046257087,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Step 1. Understand the problem and stablish\ndesign scope\n\n\nWhat kind of chat app shall we design?\nIt should support 1 on 1 and group chat\n\nIs it mobile app or web?\nBoth\n\nWhat is the scale of the app?\nIt should support 50 million DAU\n\nFor group chat what is the member limit?\n100 people\n\nWhat features are important for the chat?\n1 on 1 chat, groupt chat, online indicator. \nOnly text messages\n\nIs there a message size limit?\nyes, text len must be less than 100,000 chars\n\nHow long shall we storethe chat history?\nForever\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Step 1. Understand the problem and stablish\ndesign scope\n\n\nWhat kind of chat app shall we design?\nIt should support 1 on 1 and group chat\n\nIs it mobile app or web?\nBoth\n\nWhat is the scale of the app?\nIt should support 50 million DAU\n\nFor group chat what is the member limit?\n100 people\n\nWhat features are important for the chat?\n1 on 1 chat, groupt chat, online indicator. \nOnly text messages\n\nIs there a message size limit?\nyes, text len must be less than 100,000 chars\n\nHow long shall we storethe chat history?\nForever\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
