    {
      "id": "d3ncfTTDtNlusaKiLdOUq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 808.833251953125,
      "y": 136.83334350585938,
      "width": 750.4195556640625,
      "height": 425,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1937656481,
      "version": 697,
      "versionNonce": 885632867,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1765046257087,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Step 2. Propose high level design and get buy-in\n\nPolling: technique where the clients periodically asks the server if\nthere are messages available.\n\n\nLong poling: a client holds the connection open until there are\nactually new messages available or a timeout threshold has been reached.\nOnce it actually receives new messages, it sends anotherrequest to the\nserver\n- Sender and receiver may not connect to the same chat sever.\n- server has no good way to tell if the client is disconnected\n- It is inefficient. \n\nWebsocket\nIs the most common solution for sendin async updates from server to client.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Step 2. Propose high level design and get buy-in\n\nPolling: technique where the clients periodically asks the server if\nthere are messages available.\n\n\nLong poling: a client holds the connection open until there are\nactually new messages available or a timeout threshold has been reached.\nOnce it actually receives new messages, it sends anotherrequest to the\nserver\n- Sender and receiver may not connect to the same chat sever.\n- server has no good way to tell if the client is disconnected\n- It is inefficient. \n\nWebsocket\nIs the most common solution for sendin async updates from server to client.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
