    {
      "id": "1YhCW63JTL1GmlT5JlJHM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3453.7154036685815,
      "y": 120.51251485975416,
      "width": 791.939453125,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1c",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2045945891,
      "version": 504,
      "versionNonce": 1765586733,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1765046257087,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CLient maintains a persisten websocket connection to a chat server for real time\nmessaging\n- Chat serversfacilitate mssage sending/receiving\n- Presence servers manage online/offline status\n- API servers handle verything including user login, singup,\n- Notification servers send push notificaiton\n- key-value store is used to store chat history",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CLient maintains a persisten websocket connection to a chat server for real time\nmessaging\n- Chat serversfacilitate mssage sending/receiving\n- Presence servers manage online/offline status\n- API servers handle verything including user login, singup,\n- Notification servers send push notificaiton\n- key-value store is used to store chat history",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "vQUYbyD1oTxSO_GQs_nK7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3460.604197613894,
      "y": 327.0125758949104,
      "width": 76.29994201660156,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1d",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1850071011,
      "version": 23,
      "versionNonce": 1601134115,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1765046257087,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Storage",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Storage",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "idjzAA2cn50GXaFNgcSXp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3453.048777692019,
      "y": 376.9570339027229,
      "width": 1010.9193115234375,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1e",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 195155299,
      "version": 612,
      "versionNonce": 408373645,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1765046257087,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Selecting storage that supports all of the use cases is crucial. We recommend key-value store\n\n- Key value allows easy horizontall scalling\n- Key-value stores provide very low latency to access data\n- Relational databases do not handle long tail of data well. When the indexs grow large, random\n  access is expensive\n- Key-value are adopted by other proven reliable chat applications. For example both fb and discord use\n  it. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Selecting storage that supports all of the use cases is crucial. We recommend key-value store\n\n- Key value allows easy horizontall scalling\n- Key-value stores provide very low latency to access data\n- Relational databases do not handle long tail of data well. When the indexs grow large, random\n  access is expensive\n- Key-value are adopted by other proven reliable chat applications. For example both fb and discord use\n  it. ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
