      "seed": 2021018243,
      "version": 523,
      "versionNonce": 248553891,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1765046257087,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Service discovery\nThe primary role is to reccommend the bse chat server for a client based on the criteria \nlike geogrpahical location, serercapacity, etc.. Apache Zookeper is a popular open source\nsolution for service discovery. It registrers all the available chat servers and picks the best chat\nserver\nfor the client based on the predefined criteria.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Service discovery\nThe primary role is to reccommend the bse chat server for a client based on the criteria \nlike geogrpahical location, serercapacity, etc.. Apache Zookeper is a popular open source\nsolution for service discovery. It registrers all the available chat servers and picks the best chat server\nfor the client based on the predefined criteria.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
