      "text": "An online presence indicator is an essential feature of many chat applications.\nUsually, you can see a green dot next to a users profiel picture or username.\n\nIn high level design presence servers are responsible for managing online status and\ncommunication with clients through WebSockets. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
